  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Cook pasta according to package instructions.",
    "In a large skillet, heat olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add Irish sausage and cook until browned, breaking up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "Add onion and garlic to skillet and cook until onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in canned tomatoes and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add cooked pasta to skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer pasta mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Top with salmon fillets and sprinkle with mozzarella cheese.",
    "Bake for 15-20 minutes or until salmon is cooked through and cheese is melted.",
    "Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese and chopped basil before serving."
